Examples for qPharmetra style NONMEM data set

example.NONMEM.dataset.Rd

Examples for qPharmetra style NONMEM data set

example.NONMEM.dataset(ID = 3, TIME = seq(0, 24, 2), DOSE = c(1, 2.5, 10), ...)

Arguments

ID

number of subjects
TIME

sequence of times
DOSE

sequence of dose amounts
...

ignored

See also

Other qpexamples: example.CWRES.plot(), example.pkpdData(), example.xpose.VPC()
